# kustomize --enable-helm pulls remote charts into a local charts/ cache next to the
# kustomization (e.g. a direct `kustomize build` of a policy using helmCharts with repo:).
# The e2e/release renders use temp dirs; this only appears on a direct in-tree render.
policies/**/charts/
